				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/B%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A1t-man-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Bồ tát man kỳ 1 - 菩薩蠻其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%C3%A1n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Ho%C3%A0i-An-D%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-ORpVdmNbqly8NqnrNH_72g">Hoài An Dưỡng kỳ 3 - 懷安養其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%C3%A1n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-Ow4xyDxUryJNvfkJIR1oyg">Nhật Quán thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Nh%C3%A3n-ph%C3%B3ng-thanh/poem-vWn4J22hFVU6OjlhYoOREw">Nhãn phóng thanh - 眼放青</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/Ph%E1%BB%A5c-k%C3%BD-Y%C3%AAn-Kinh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-HI6oO9C2N4VRcgKueOaf5A">Phục ký Yên Kinh đạo hữu - 復寄燕京道友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/author-Xdrx9PY_HQVilIv5qP5QxQ">Khâu Xứ Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Ti%E1%BB%83u-H%E1%BA%A7u-H%E1%BA%A3i/poem-GOjxX3WrbeVYR50HQYCb7A">Tặng Tiểu Hầu (Hải) - 贈小候（海）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thanh-minh/poem-3YDWV6YBQVyQBygAwpaO-g">Thanh minh - 清明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-K%E1%BA%BF/T%C3%ADch-ni%C3%AAn-kim-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%C3%A1o-C%C3%B4n-L%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-k8er4EOZAhmKGP0aYJMslA">Tích niên kim nhật đáo Côn Lôn kỳ 3 - 昔年今日到崑崙其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-K%E1%BA%BF/author-SslMhW8LozZDjTCazfC2iQ">Ngô Đức Kế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Giai/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-c%C3%B4ng-chi-%C4%90oan-H%C3%B9ng/poem-VEWFzIoIrYX9-wuAdMH53w">Tiễn Phạm công chi Đoan Hùng - 餞范公之端雄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Giai/author-tbVETc5SFc0ZkdKBtLYjiw">Nguyễn Công Giai</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-H%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A2n-tr%C3%BAc/poem-S_6Ep_TA4G4Lx5vZOW-aGA">Vịnh Đông Hồ tân trúc - 詠東湖新竹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Xu%C3%A2n-ng%C3%A2m/poem-Rfa7C6A_POegZiuLVghWiQ">Xuân ngâm - 春吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
